WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:09.500
Royal icing made with powdered egg whites

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:13.000
35 ml water

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:16.000
A pinch of cream of tartar

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:19.000
1 teaspoon extract

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:22.000
7 g albumen (powdered egg white)

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:25.000
250 g icing sugar

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:30.000
Put half of the sugar into the bowl

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:35.000
Add powdered egg white

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:45.000
Mix at low speed

00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:54.000
Add water

00:00:54.000 --> 00:00:57.000
a pinch of cream of tartar

00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:01.000
and a teaspoon extract

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:08.000
Mix at low speed

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:19.000
Add remaining sugar

00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:28.000
Mix again until smooth

00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:50.000
Keep in an airtight container

00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:55.000
Can be stored in the refrigerator for 15 days

00:01:55.000 --> 00:01:59.000
This royal icing can be used as edible glue for your sugar decorations

00:01:59.000 --> 00:02:02.500
and mixed with water can be used to glaze cookies 

